Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a BETA version.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.22,0:00:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go to Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the Rising Star's Christmas performance is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go to Europe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't know the reason why she\Nparticipates in the competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to catch up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that determination she arrived at this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Such a messy playing..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's wrong with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that she forgets that she still has one\Nmore piece to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Debussy..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine more enjoyable things!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like being in love....feeling good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being in love....feel good??
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Debussy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,went to an island in the south with his lover,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and composed this piece feeling a lot of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up to now you were walking on a tightrope, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!\NThe sounds are glittering...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Debussy being lost in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's expressing it very well!\NAuclair Sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she is not expressing that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps she's still a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we are going to announce the result\Nof the Second Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.85,0:03:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda Megumi\NNo.28
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The numbers of the performers who can\Nproceed to the Final Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number eight, number eight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuboi-kun, congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaaaaa!!\NYuu-kun, Yuu-kun, Yuu-kun! Congratulations!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,28.....28....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,28, be in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's there!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's there~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good, it's good, isn't it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I wouldn't make it..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and see the Final Stage too,\Nso do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do our best too
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still some things in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show I can definitely get the 1st place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame Cantabile\NLesson 10
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This softsubs only for home use.\NDo not distribute.\Nhttp://s-projects.org
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard that there'll be an audition
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us take the audition too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if only for a reserve, I don't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have practiced very hard to be able to get\Ninto Rising Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold an audition when the piece needs many players,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,therefore practice as hard as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WAIT A MINUTE!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:06:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's my Oke,\Nyou can enter it right away now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second famous in this Academy, Ookouchi Mamoru's\Nspecial orchestra,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,abbreviated as..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O...\N(O.M.S Oke = Ookuchi Mamoru Special Oke)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but could you please hurry up\Nwearing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Publicity photo for the Christmas performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we print and distribute it today,\Nit won't be on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I had better change my clothes too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the advertisement, I'm thinking of only\Nemphasizing the good-looking ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't\Nmind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun, there's a music room over there,\Nchange your clothes in that room, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was not informed about this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, or else it will be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-kun, as this will be the last,\Nwhat about changing your clothes here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I help you change your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, OK I'll go to that room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh! New East Philharmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly there was a recruitment for\Na timpani player, and when I applied to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed through the document selection!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.95,0:06:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next steps will be the exam for practical\Nskill and the final interview!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heeeh, that's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Masumi-chan's dream to join a\Nprofessional Oke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I pass the exam, it means I will be\Nplaying double with Rising Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're playing double, you can\Ncontinue to be in Rising Star, isn't it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyora
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your concert last time was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This spring you will be coming to Vienna, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will set aside my time for your sake,\Nand I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-ka-ka-ka-ka-ka....Kai Dune Sensei\Ndirectly praised you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, that's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Ryuu-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haiiiii...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sales for our Christmas performance tickets\Nseem to be very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An everlasting orchestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the second step to my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuutaro, umm.....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, let's tell Chiaki about it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Where is he now?? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.41,0:07:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Chiakiiiiii!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Chiaki-kun, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me join your Oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm violin player Takahashi Noriyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyora, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won 3rd place in last year's\NBuffon International Violin Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was studying in Paris, but last month\NI returned to Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My experience in orchestra is just a little\Nwhile in the University over there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if these aren't enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm NOT below this Oke's\NConcert Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What??!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.57,0:08:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, Kiyora...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3rd place in Buffon International?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, didn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say your name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that! Hurry up take off your clothes,\NI can't barely wait anymore!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MASUMI-CHAN!!!!\NCHIAKI-KUN'S IN DANGER!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wohhhhh!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Samaaaaa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, who are you?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the Finals, play Schumann's Piano Sonata no2 and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stravinsky's Petrouchka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Petrouchka..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must finish these two pieces by the day after tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect that you would pass through\Nuntil the Final Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,up to now it was like walking on a tightrope\Nthat we managed to arrive to this stage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time left for you to master\Ntwo pieces perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why on the opposite,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I selected two pieces having high level of difficulties,\Nso that you can appeal using your technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, as befitting of him.\NUnless one is no 3 in Buffon International Competition.....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High-level technique, various vibrato, fast passage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,very firm,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thorough, and detailed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dynamic and passionate,\Na different type of player from Kiyora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's your decision, Chiaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl, or me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which one is more suitable to become\Nthe Concert Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came here to take an audition, didn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you suddenly want to be the Concert Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Mojya mojya!\N(=afro hair)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got an invitation from the entertainment biz, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if I can enter this Oke, I'll reject their offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I should at least get the Concert Master\Nposition here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entertainment biz?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's already a sure thing, why would you reject them,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and prefer to enter our Oke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this Oke is great, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, my heart beat faster\Nafter not experiencing it for a long while!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody is skillful,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,young, confident, and looked to enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if a lot of sounds are making love...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this beautiful Conductor giving himself to ecstasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and young guys in tuxedos...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaaaa....how should I explain it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I love clasical music!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I love this Oke especially!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I love Chiaki-kun too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, the last thing you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already have....\N(throwing salt to drive away evil)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a wonderful Concert Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm touched by your enthusiasm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today, you're a member of the Rising Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Ryuu-chan! All of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Takahashi-kun's performance doesn't\Nhave power as big as as Kiyora's,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he has detailed technique, beautiful echo,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his level is higher than Kiyora's!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather than no 2 in National Competition,\Nno 3 in Buffon International Competition will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,better for our Oke's advertisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, Kiyora,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't hesitate anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can wholeheartedly return to Vienna
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then someday, if you want to become this Oke's\NConcert Master once again,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.70,0:12:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bring back with you 2 or 3 better titles\Nthan this guy has!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will practice violin so hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I won't have any time left to cheat on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? EHHH???
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama, you're not very keen, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.54,0:12:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will certainly keep this Oke going!\NWhat about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will certainly keep this Oke going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,regardless how many of you will leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will keep it going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, like that please.\NHai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't be a stagnant orchestra,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but an orchestra that will progress with time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!\NBye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Venus is rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, Chiaki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, in order to deepen our friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's the two of us have a chat until morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Samaaaa!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama, hurry up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this chance to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masumi, you followed me for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must do my part too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:14:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Chiaki-kun! What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask concerning\Nthe Rising Star
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another one who's progressing\Nin a dizzy way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.77,0:14:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second finger was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rhythm was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so, Schumann?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to eat lunch properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't eaten anything since yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan, what's that??
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must take a rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:15:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or take some fresh air outside!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. Noda Megumi? She passed the 2nd stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 18th Maradonna Piano Competition\NCompetitors for the Final Stage:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4th year Tsuboi Ryuuji\N3rd year Noda Megumi
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame, all of a sudden..?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eto Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.29,0:15:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Nodame?\NCan she win?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.04,0:15:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unknown yet whether Noda will finish\Npractising it till the Final Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today she'll have to practice until midnight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, Schumann...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That one will sure take time to master..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh??
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She already mastered it!\NHow come so sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan was doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what it means
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this one is plus and this one is minus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Electrical charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone come and teach her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaaa, please don't say such a scary thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.54,0:16:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody came!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan kept practising by herself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She kept repeating the same Movement over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and blah blah blah speaking to herself.....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,electrical charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these, actually!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I thought that she was playing Schubert messily,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the next day suddenly she could play it correctly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I thought she could manage to play\Na difficult piece perfectly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on stage, that was....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of kid is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The no-good version again??
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the experience of having such\Na pupil like her before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I teach her..geeezz!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, Noda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KAORI!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.63,0:18:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saiko..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were studying just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.87,0:18:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually I have some business with\Nyour neighbor next door, but she seems to be out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My neighbor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give it to her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas Concert\NR.S Orchestra\NDecember 25th, 2006 Suntory Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because that girl seems to be trying hard to do\Nher best
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to do a few things in the past because\NI wanted Shinichi to love me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to be able to walk side by side with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she is trying so very hard to catch up with you, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be great if she can do well in the\NFinal Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi too..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be your last performance in japan, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First floor, 12th row, Seat no 19\N5000 yen\N(good seat)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,38.8 Celcius?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Kozo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we had better take her to hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is already very late...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the time being let her rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:19:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we still have antipiretics?\N(=medicine to reduce fever)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because she's always strange
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so when she's really strange like now, I didn't notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's forcing herself too much
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she didn't even eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at a time when, because of the competition,\Nthe peak of exhaustion should be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, it is completely time-over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever can go through those Petrouchka rings gets\N2000.000 yen prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame will go through them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it in advance
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you miss it, you'll be punished\Nby swallowing 1000 needles!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.93,0:21:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew it too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, you were in that room,\Nright? Megumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Petrouchka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.27,0:21:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stravinsky, who was a pianist and conductor,\Nchanged this orchestra piece
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into a piano piece for the sake of a ballet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An orchestra piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sad story about a puppet,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.14,0:22:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who after given life by the puppeteer,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,eventually wished to be a real human.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.00,0:22:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this piece is like a festival in a\Nlively toyland...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.29,0:22:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you have good ears,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.65,0:22:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan!\NIt's time already!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.85,0:22:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go to the competition hall!\NWe have to rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a bit more....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One complete song...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't make it in time....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.27,0:22:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't given up, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that ringtone?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's Cooking, Today's Cooking!\N(=a TV show, the song is its theme song)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.04,0:23:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! We arrived!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda, let's get off!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.02,0:23:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Nodame-chan!!\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda!\NYou really did it well!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you shouldn't perform the 2nd piece in\Nsuch a condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.62,0:23:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you fail....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.83,0:23:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.92,0:23:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you finish playing the first piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.37,0:23:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leave the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.04,0:23:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.52,0:24:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.07,0:24:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maradonna Piano Competition\NFinal Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.11,0:24:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, you have to change your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.81,0:24:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of the Final Stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.75,0:24:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the level is high!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.92,0:24:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I started to feel very tense!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.73,0:24:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Nodame-chan be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.13,0:24:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,28. Noda Megumi\NSchumann/Piano Sonata No2\NStravinsky/Petrouchka
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.66,0:24:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.86,0:24:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mouth..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.64,0:25:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clown face Megumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.36,0:25:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clown face?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.13,0:25:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were still playing the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.68,0:25:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so surprised to see you in competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.36,0:25:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, Hanasakura Sensei also came here to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.90,0:25:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ehh, Petrouchka...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.22,0:25:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can play such a piece already!\NHow wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.84,0:25:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.37,0:25:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...won't be defeated by you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.89,0:25:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow,  once a person passes 20 years old,\Nshe's just a usual person...they said!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.84,0:25:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he was a candidate to win 1st place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.02,0:25:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it!! What an appearance!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.66,0:26:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's skillful!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.15,0:26:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The echo of the chord is good
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.51,0:26:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling of the variation part also\Ncomes out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.57,0:26:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that obasan! What a person!!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.48,0:27:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Not a single miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.66,0:27:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,21. Yuuto Segawa\N21 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.51,0:27:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...what is it that he is scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.56,0:27:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.74,0:27:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must aim higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.03,0:27:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly to the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.74,0:27:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hand is wrong! This hand!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.63,0:27:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Nodame, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.37,0:27:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of performance is she\Ngoing to give?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.56,0:28:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schumann and Stravinsky..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.11,0:28:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two pieces....
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.23,0:28:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can she really play them?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.20,0:28:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.89,0:28:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haaa?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.09,0:28:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scarlett O'Hara?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.57,0:28:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.67,0:28:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your forte is being surpassed, Masumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.65,0:28:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to catch up with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.55,0:29:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she did her best to arrive at this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.94,0:29:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh God, please bless her!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.83,0:29:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She, all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.52,0:29:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,playing it as if the urgency of the rhythm is clinging on her...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.35,0:29:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a complete Schumann...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.86,0:30:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my first time....
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.79,0:30:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to see her performing like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.67,0:30:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose control, Baby-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.89,0:30:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it which you want so much,\Nthat you came to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.96,0:31:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still one piece left, but the audience\Nalready......
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.09,0:31:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kozo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.03,0:31:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.35,0:31:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.03,0:31:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop here!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.64,0:31:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up now....and bow to the audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.24,0:31:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.89,0:31:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.22,0:31:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, not yet, there is still more you can do, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.66,0:32:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She plays it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.98,0:32:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An active piece with a lot of notes...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.61,0:32:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her versatile sounds are being drawn out
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.69,0:32:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is completely..
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.58,0:32:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the sounds of an orchestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.77,0:32:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Todays' Cooking"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.54,0:32:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She stops!!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.46,0:33:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened with Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.95,0:33:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not Petrouchka!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.37,0:33:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, back again now!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.54,0:33:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's composing her own piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.78,0:34:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She recovered in the later part..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.62,0:35:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BRAVO!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.36,0:35:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi Noda\NNo 28
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.64,0:35:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi Noda...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.10,0:35:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was a good performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.42,0:35:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,changing the piece is not allowed in competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.52,0:35:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it means that she couldn't master\Nthe piece on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.47,0:35:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.65,0:36:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda Megumi\NNo.28
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.74,0:36:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fourth place: no 8, Tsuboi Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.70,0:36:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third place: no 10......Sakake Shouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.87,0:36:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First place: No one!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.35,0:36:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second place: No 21, Segawa Yuuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.71,0:36:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why there is no one for First Place?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.11,0:36:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.27,0:37:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you go to Europe together with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.54,0:37:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to continue your piano,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.51,0:37:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather than our school,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.01,0:37:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the school abroad will suit you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.91,0:37:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover there are scholarship organizations,\Nand other competitions,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.00,0:37:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,go abroad,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.99,0:37:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and see more,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.85,0:37:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,feel more, experience more....
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.61,0:37:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,together with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.09,0:37:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.83,0:37:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to study to the extent of\Ndoing all those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.65,0:37:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.12,0:37:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.09,0:37:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've become serious with piano, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.66,0:38:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you took part in the Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.88,0:38:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I joined the Competition just to get the prize money.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.50,0:38:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I wanted money.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.20,0:38:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the desire to have the money to play around!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.49,0:38:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.02,0:38:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do or say the way you wanted it to!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.24,0:38:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,always, always, since a long time ago..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.84,0:38:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must aim higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.52,0:38:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly to the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.80,0:38:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fed up with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.36,0:38:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with playing the piano freely\Nand the way I enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.76,0:38:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.72,0:38:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You....
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.75,0:38:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in that competition..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.80,0:38:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,playing the piano on the stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.33,0:38:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,really, didn't you enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.08,0:39:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.01,0:39:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.05,0:39:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.65,0:39:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.73,0:39:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was the first time I saw you facing\Nmusic so seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.19,0:39:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a very good performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.09,0:40:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.84,0:40:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't win, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.84,0:40:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chinese Food\NUraken
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.43,0:40:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Several days later
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.17,0:40:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do...my grade-up exam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.42,0:40:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uraken Original Christmas Cake\NReceiving order until 12/25!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.89,0:40:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head was so full of the Christmas Concert
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.36,0:40:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I forgot about the exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.23,0:40:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you yourself who said you\Nwanted to do Christmas Concert, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.93,0:40:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't all of you stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.32,0:40:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody also has exams, don't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.53,0:40:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who haven't studied to the\Npoint that you panicked just before the exams!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.81,0:40:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack, shall I help you?\NWhat's the subject, German?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.59,0:40:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'll let you think I'm stupid concerning\Nmy study too, huh??
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.46,0:40:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but you're really stupid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.84,0:40:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.43,0:40:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Chiaki, can you please teach me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.66,0:40:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.56,0:40:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please, even if just my subdivision, the piano..
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.57,0:40:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.32,0:40:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also busy myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.66,0:40:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuutaro! If it's piano, what about asking Nodame-chan\Nto teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.29,0:40:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Dad, that's a good idea you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.19,0:40:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, but how is she doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.06,0:40:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, I wonder if she's feeling down now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.64,0:41:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.20,0:41:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from her room,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.98,0:41:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even the sounds of piano never come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.28,0:41:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.18,0:41:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sakuma here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.24,0:41:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the matter you asked me the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.66,0:41:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.41,0:41:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning excellent conductors who might be able\Nto replace Chiaki-kun as the conductor of the Rising Star
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.18,0:41:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have listed several of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.72,0:41:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring it with me next time, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.32,0:41:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda Yukihisa (28 years old)
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.70,0:41:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.37,0:41:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must tell all of them properly
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.12,0:42:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about my going away..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.78,0:42:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[Today's Practice]\NIn use by R.S Orchestra
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.76,0:42:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!\NHi, Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.84,0:42:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.12,0:42:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning our Chrsitmas performance\Nat Suntory Hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.98,0:42:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have decided on the other piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.21,0:42:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of practising it directly\Nin our next practice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.71,0:42:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The piece is..
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.58,0:42:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beethoven's No 7, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.65,0:42:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.32,0:42:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.79,0:42:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be lively too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.79,0:42:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, I like this piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.04,0:42:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody already practiced it in advance, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.73,0:42:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.68,0:42:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.90,0:42:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why....why did everybody know it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.95,0:42:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.23,0:42:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already heard it from Mine-kun quite sometime ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.16,0:42:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.28,0:43:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first piece we performed in S-Oke, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.73,0:43:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's the first piece Chiaki-Sama conducted!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.00,0:43:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the start of everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.76,0:43:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's perform it perfectly,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.28,0:43:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will be Chiaki's last conducting in Rising Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.04,0:43:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine....
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.46,0:43:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time left, let's begin our practice now!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.28,0:43:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.95,0:44:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.11,0:44:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.84,0:45:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MERRY CHRISTMAS!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.95,0:45:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,http://s-projects.org